1
00:00:23,359 --> 00:00:24,679
Look at you,

2
00:00:25,039 --> 00:00:27,000
you look like a compassionate goddess.

3
00:00:27,600 --> 00:00:28,199
Sis,

4
00:00:29,140 --> 00:00:30,320
do I have to

5
00:00:31,000 --> 00:00:32,500
go to the Treasure House?

6
00:00:34,460 --> 00:00:36,460
It's a dangerous place,

7
00:00:38,179 --> 00:00:40,020
but it's our only shortcut.

8
00:00:43,119 --> 00:00:43,679
Don't be afraid.

9
00:00:44,700 --> 00:00:46,500
I'll be there for you.

10
00:00:49,460 --> 00:00:50,100
[Lady An,]

11
00:00:50,460 --> 00:00:51,380
[please come out.]

12
00:00:52,560 --> 00:00:53,159
Remember,

13
00:00:53,380 --> 00:00:54,340
follow the plan.

14
00:01:11,579 --> 00:01:12,140
General,

15
00:01:13,060 --> 00:01:13,879
setting a fire to force her out,

16
00:01:14,260 --> 00:01:14,980
if she is

17
00:01:14,980 --> 00:01:16,260
the one the Queen Mother wants,

18
00:01:16,340 --> 00:01:16,780
then

19
00:01:17,040 --> 00:01:18,200
with her skills,

20
00:01:19,340 --> 00:01:21,260
she must have a way to escape.

21
00:01:25,640 --> 00:01:26,359
I

22
00:01:26,359 --> 00:01:28,620
tear off her mask myself.

23
00:01:35,379 --> 00:01:35,900
General,

24
00:01:36,340 --> 00:01:37,299
there's no sound inside.

25
00:01:37,640 --> 00:01:38,159
What if...

26
00:01:40,500 --> 00:01:41,939
[I'd rather die than expose myself.]

27
00:01:43,400 --> 00:01:45,459
[What exactly are your intentions?]

28
00:01:47,060 --> 00:01:47,739
[Sister,]

29
00:01:48,060 --> 00:01:49,400
[come and save me.]

30
00:03:01,180 --> 00:03:01,819
You can come down now.

31
00:03:09,620 --> 00:03:11,360
Thank you for saving me, General.

32
00:03:12,340 --> 00:03:13,020
Your shoulder...

33
00:03:22,680 --> 00:03:24,020
I have no home now.

34
00:03:25,719 --> 00:03:27,599
I can only follow you to the capital.

35
00:03:28,479 --> 00:03:29,759
After joining the Treasure House,

36
00:03:30,240 --> 00:03:31,479
I hope you can

37
00:03:32,400 --> 00:03:33,400
take care of me.

38
00:03:34,159 --> 00:03:34,879
Take care of you?

39
00:03:36,159 --> 00:03:36,840
My duty

40
00:03:37,280 --> 00:03:39,099
is to escort treasures to the warehouse.

41
00:03:40,199 --> 00:03:41,780
Your life is none of my business.

42
00:03:42,979 --> 00:03:43,479
Xie Mo.
Yes, sir.

43
00:03:44,439 --> 00:03:44,919
Take him away.
Lady An,

44
00:03:46,240 --> 00:03:46,639
this way please.

45
00:03:56,520 --> 00:03:58,199
[She doesn't seem to be pretending.]

46
00:03:59,460 --> 00:04:00,900
[Even if she's not Su Luoyao,]

47
00:04:01,039 --> 00:04:02,080
[she must be a close relative.]

48
00:04:03,219 --> 00:04:04,780
[I can't let my guard down.]

49
00:04:12,139 --> 00:04:13,099
This way, please.

50
00:04:16,779 --> 00:04:17,899
Our temple is humble

51
00:04:18,620 --> 00:04:19,819
and has been without incense for a long time.

52
00:04:20,220 --> 00:04:21,699
I'm sorry to have neglected you.

53
00:04:21,959 --> 00:04:22,720
Thank you, Master.

54
00:04:23,019 --> 00:04:24,220
We'll rest here for the night.

55
00:04:24,420 --> 00:04:25,540
We'll set off at dawn tomorrow.

56
00:04:28,819 --> 00:04:29,240
This...

57
00:04:30,100 --> 00:04:31,779
This is an ominous object.

58
00:04:33,939 --> 00:04:34,259
This...

59
00:04:36,180 --> 00:04:36,500
Master,

60
00:04:37,379 --> 00:04:38,259
is there anything wrong?

61
00:04:38,740 --> 00:04:41,540
It's... it's too similar.

62
00:04:42,139 --> 00:04:42,980
Eight years ago,

63
00:04:43,500 --> 00:04:45,199
it was a box like this.

64
00:04:46,699 --> 00:04:47,139
It's like...

65
00:04:47,579 --> 00:04:49,660
It's like a coffin.

66
00:04:59,000 --> 00:05:01,379
The moon was bright that night.

67
00:05:02,759 --> 00:05:03,819
When the wind blew,

68
00:05:04,639 --> 00:05:06,199
it brought with it

69
00:05:06,259 --> 00:05:08,639
a smell of blood that seeped into the bones.

70
00:05:10,079 --> 00:05:12,040
I followed the trail of blood

71
00:05:13,860 --> 00:05:15,360
all the way to the temple.

72
00:05:16,300 --> 00:05:17,240
From afar,

73
00:05:17,920 --> 00:05:18,399
I saw

74
00:05:18,399 --> 00:05:19,420
a chest like this

75
00:05:19,420 --> 00:05:20,259
lying there,

76
00:05:21,680 --> 00:05:25,279
surrounded by soldiers' corpses.

77
00:05:25,939 --> 00:05:27,439
The blood flowed like a river,

78
00:05:27,579 --> 00:05:28,540
even the moon

79
00:05:28,740 --> 00:05:30,220
was stained red.

80
00:05:30,740 --> 00:05:32,300
Did you see the murderer?

81
00:05:32,680 --> 00:05:33,519
Amitabha.

82
00:05:34,639 --> 00:05:35,480
The murderer

83
00:05:47,000 --> 00:05:47,639
is a demon from a painting.

84
00:05:48,779 --> 00:05:49,620
Amitabha.
Amitabha.

85
00:05:50,699 --> 00:05:51,740
Amitabha.

86
00:05:54,240 --> 00:05:55,959
Amitabha.

87
00:05:56,420 --> 00:05:57,259
Amitabha.

88
00:06:01,759 --> 00:06:02,519
[Eight years ago,]

89
00:06:02,519 --> 00:06:04,420
[what secrets were hidden?]

90
00:06:21,500 --> 00:06:22,439
[Who are you?]

91
00:06:23,300 --> 00:06:24,620
[What are you plotting?]

92
00:06:29,060 --> 00:06:29,699
Poisonous smoke.

93
00:06:51,379 --> 00:06:52,420
Silk threads.

94
00:06:53,660 --> 00:06:54,379
Damn it.

95
00:06:55,339 --> 00:06:56,519
It's the night of the full moon.

96
00:07:09,180 --> 00:07:11,060
The ill-gotten gains of the Bureau of Treasures

97
00:07:11,259 --> 00:07:12,500
will be accepted by the Nonuple Palace.

98
00:07:13,240 --> 00:07:15,000
Thank you for your gift.

99
00:07:29,040 --> 00:07:29,959
Little slave,

100
00:07:30,740 --> 00:07:32,220
running around on the night of the full moon

101
00:07:34,860 --> 00:07:36,420
can get you killed.

102
00:07:44,779 --> 00:07:45,259
Retreat!

103
00:07:47,980 --> 00:07:50,060
Antidote...

104
00:07:53,220 --> 00:07:56,300
When asking for help, show respect.

105
00:08:01,920 --> 00:08:02,879
Speak up!

106
00:08:04,360 --> 00:08:05,360
Master,

107
00:08:05,980 --> 00:08:07,240
I'm begging you!

108
00:08:12,939 --> 00:08:14,160
Master!

109
00:08:41,019 --> 00:08:41,759
See?

110
00:08:42,399 --> 00:08:43,139
Only your master

111
00:08:43,139 --> 00:08:44,860
can save you.

112
00:08:52,000 --> 00:08:53,600
There's no way to untangle the silk.

113
00:08:56,500 --> 00:08:57,340
I

114
00:08:58,799 --> 00:09:00,440
am your only way out.

115
00:09:19,779 --> 00:09:20,519
Stop it!

116
00:09:20,740 --> 00:09:22,620
A child playing with fire will wet the bed.

117
00:09:23,220 --> 00:09:24,659
You're the one who wets the bed!

118
00:09:27,139 --> 00:09:27,460
My Lord,

119
00:09:28,820 --> 00:09:29,580
when Xie Lingfeng

120
00:09:29,980 --> 00:09:31,259
heard about the tragedy eight years ago,

121
00:09:32,059 --> 00:09:33,220
his expression changed instantly.

122
00:09:33,899 --> 00:09:34,580
He must know something.

123
00:09:35,600 --> 00:09:36,919
He deserves to die.

124
00:09:37,500 --> 00:09:37,860
My Lord,

125
00:09:38,659 --> 00:09:39,620
why do you keep him alive?

126
00:09:41,379 --> 00:09:42,259
Is it because

127
00:09:42,740 --> 00:09:44,860
he's good-looking

128
00:09:45,419 --> 00:09:46,500
and you have a soft spot for him?

129
00:09:47,440 --> 00:09:48,519
He's too cunning for his age.

130
00:09:53,779 --> 00:09:54,419
Eight years ago,

131
00:09:55,299 --> 00:09:56,539
the Xies committed a massacre,

132
00:09:57,480 --> 00:09:58,240
causing our loved ones

133
00:09:58,240 --> 00:09:59,259
to suffer unjustly.

134
00:10:00,299 --> 00:10:01,299
[Only the blood of the Xie family]

135
00:10:01,899 --> 00:10:03,200
[can wash away]

136
00:10:03,200 --> 00:10:04,100
[this grievance.]

137
00:10:05,500 --> 00:10:06,500
[Until then,]

138
00:10:08,799 --> 00:10:10,279
[every moment I live]

139
00:10:10,700 --> 00:10:12,179
[is to send them]

140
00:10:12,879 --> 00:10:13,899
[to hell.]

141
00:10:16,580 --> 00:10:17,980
[Xie Lingfeng is just the beginning.]

142
00:10:19,139 --> 00:10:20,539
[The real key]

143
00:10:22,179 --> 00:10:23,580
[is Xie Huaiyun's]

144
00:10:24,980 --> 00:10:26,139
[Bai Zhen Dept.]

145
00:10:45,379 --> 00:10:46,220
General,

146
00:10:49,460 --> 00:10:50,899
I accidentally got this wound

147
00:10:50,899 --> 00:10:52,580
when I was helping the abbot

148
00:10:52,720 --> 00:10:53,600
repair the statue last night.

149
00:10:59,620 --> 00:11:01,779
It's really fine.

150
00:11:03,980 --> 00:11:06,220
Thank you for your concern.

151
00:11:07,379 --> 00:11:08,059
Concern?

152
00:11:09,179 --> 00:11:10,019
I was just thinking

153
00:11:10,019 --> 00:11:12,700
that the location of the wound is quite coincidental.

154
00:11:16,179 --> 00:11:16,700
Xie Mo.
Yes.

155
00:11:18,860 --> 00:11:20,980
Take Lady An and get ready to go.

156
00:11:21,460 --> 00:11:21,879
Lady An,
this way, please.

157
00:11:34,860 --> 00:11:35,139
If it weren't for

158
00:11:35,139 --> 00:11:36,200
the woman in red

159
00:11:36,200 --> 00:11:36,899
suddenly interfering,
the remaining chests

160
00:11:38,580 --> 00:11:39,419
would be ours.

161
00:11:41,139 --> 00:11:42,379
That woman is cunning.

162
00:11:42,820 --> 00:11:43,899
How was your night, My Lord?

163
00:11:46,580 --> 00:11:47,139
Lord,

164
00:11:47,679 --> 00:11:49,159
you were quite agile last night.

165
00:11:49,480 --> 00:11:50,620
As for these treasures,

166
00:11:50,620 --> 00:11:52,460
just distribute them to the poor as usual.

167
00:11:53,019 --> 00:11:53,580
Rest assured, Lord.

168
00:11:54,100 --> 00:11:55,240
The Ji Yao Pavilion and the Treasure House

169
00:11:55,240 --> 00:11:56,399
have been competing with the Xie family for years.

170
00:11:57,220 --> 00:11:58,779
We are already skilled at these things.

171
00:11:58,940 --> 00:11:59,539
There will be no mistakes.

172
00:12:00,820 --> 00:12:01,259
Lord,

173
00:12:01,700 --> 00:12:02,559
that woman in red,

174
00:12:03,019 --> 00:12:04,139
seems to know you.

175
00:12:15,940 --> 00:12:17,059
[The Treasure House,]

176
00:12:18,220 --> 00:12:20,259
[the place that imprisoned me for half my life.]

177
00:12:57,580 --> 00:12:58,740
[Su Luoyao,]

178
00:12:59,500 --> 00:13:00,899
[how much do you know]

179
00:13:01,820 --> 00:13:03,740
[about the murder eight years ago?]
